1
00:00:00,495 --> 00:00:05,755
As is known, ISIS entered Mosul in full control

2
00:00:05,780 --> 00:00:08,281
And imposed its authority over the city

3
00:00:08,306 --> 00:00:10,599
On June 10, 2014

4
00:00:11,120 --> 00:00:18,489
A few weeks later, specifically on June 15 or 20

5
00:00:18,514 --> 00:00:24,166
ISIS members began using churches as their bases

6
00:00:24,557 --> 00:00:31,406
And in the years that followed, these churches became ISIS centers

7
00:00:32,083 --> 00:00:35,729
They carried out fatwas through them

8
00:00:35,754 --> 00:00:38,672
And directives issued by ISIS

9
00:00:38,891 --> 00:00:46,026
As we can see, there are piles of satellite receivers

10
00:00:46,339 --> 00:00:52,381
ISIS took them from residents living near this area

11
00:00:52,641 --> 00:00:58,344
They were confiscated to prevent the people of Mosul from outside contact

12
00:00:58,369 --> 00:01:04,516
And from learning about the efforts of the security forces to reach the city

13
00:01:04,541 --> 00:01:06,990
And liberate it from ISIS’s grip
